    "Winter brings cold mornings and dark evenings, but it also brings Christmas, hot chocolate, and the exciting possibility of snow. When snow does fall, the whole world goes quiet and white. Everything looks clean and new. I think each season is a chapter in a long story, and I would not want to miss a single one."
